===Noun===
'''temporal case'''

#{{grammar}}: noun [[case]] used to specify a time. In English, this is usually expressed by the preposition "at," as in "'''at''' six o’clock," "'''at''' midnight," "'''at''' Christmas." [[Hungarian]] is a language that uses the temporal case.

